<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752841>
    dc:description "Figs. 11-14. Isoperla evanescens sp. n. Virginia, Bland Co., Wolf Creek. 11. Ovum. 12. Ovum, showing concave section. 13. Detail of ovum reticulations and punctuations. 14. Detail of ovum chorion and micropyles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752841/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752845>
    dc:description "Figs. 16-19. Isoperla evanescens sp. n. Virginia, Smyth Co., North Fork Holston River. 16. Nymphal head, dorsal. 17. Nymphal abdomen, dorsal. 18. Nymphal left lacinia, dorsal: A. submarginal setae. 19. Nymphal left mandible, dorsal: A. dorsal apical tooth and ventral apical tooth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752845/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752849>
    dc:description "Fig 20. Type locality. Virginia, Bland Co., Wolf Creek, Grapefield Road." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752849/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752835>
    dc:description "Figs. 5-8. Isoperla evanescens, sp. n., Virginia, Bland Co., Wolf Creek. 5. Aedeagus, lateral: A. anterodorsal lobe, B. dorsal lobe, C. posterodorsal lobe, D. paired posterolateral lobes, E. posteroventral lobe, F. basal setal band. 6. Aedeagus, posterior. 7. Paraproct, posterior. 8. Posteromedial sclerotized structure of aedeagus with ca. 10 short spines and scallop shaped setae, posterolateral, Isoperla evanescens sp. n., Virginia, Russell Co., Carr Creek." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752833>
    dc:description "Figs. 2-4. Isoperla evanescens, sp. n., holotype male. Virginia, Bland Co., Wolf Creek. 2. Head and pronotum, dorsal. 3. Abdomen and paraprocts, dorsal. 4. Abdomen and vesicle, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752833/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4752837>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Male paraproct apex, lateral, Isoperla evanescens sp. n. Virginia, Bland Co., Wolf Creek." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4752837/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

